{
  "texts": [
    "Non-English claims see a large boost when translated to English before being fed to the models.",
    "We find no sudden decrease in accuracy after the official training cutoff dates for GPT-3.5 and GPT-4.",
    "This suggests that the continued learning from human feedback may expand these models' knowledge.",
    "This paper contributes to both the evidence retrieval and claim verification steps of the automated fact-checking pipeline.",
    "Our approach focuses on verifying claims-assessing if a statement is true or false, while simultaneously retrieving contextual information to augment the ability of the LLM to reason about the given claims."
  ]
}